AI Memory Orchestrator (AMO)
Copyright 2026 Eliuth Chavero Jasso

AMO is a Git-native repository memory layer, graph system, and context compiler for AI coding agents.

The names "AI Memory Orchestrator" and "AMO", and the project positioning "The cure for context rot in AI coding agents", are associated with the original project created by Eliuth Chavero Jasso.

This product includes software developed by Eliuth Chavero Jasso and contributors.
